# Token Application

The token application is the main blockchain/cryptocurrency application in the monorepo.

## Structure

- [apps/token/src/](mdc:apps/token/src) - Main source code
  - [apps/token/src/components/](mdc:apps/token/src/components) - UI components
  - [apps/token/src/containers/](mdc:apps/token/src/containers) - Container components
  - [apps/token/src/pages/](mdc:apps/token/src/pages) - Next.js pages
  - [apps/token/src/common/](mdc:apps/token/src/common) - Shared utilities and types
  - [apps/token/src/services/](mdc:apps/token/src/services) - Service layer

## Key Features

- Blockchain Integration: [apps/token/src/services/crypto/](mdc:apps/token/src/services/crypto)
- API Endpoints: [apps/token/src/pages/api/](mdc:apps/token/src/pages/api)
- Database Models: [apps/token/prisma/](mdc:apps/token/prisma)
- Authentication: [apps/token/src/pages/api/auth/](mdc:apps/token/src/pages/api/auth)

## Database Migrations

Database migrations are stored in [apps/token/prisma/migrations/](mdc:apps/token/prisma/migrations)
